data.description:
Welcome to your dream home south of 98 with Gulf Views or rental income producing vacation home in Miramar beach! 2023 it produced $185,000 in rental income!!! 2024 projection is 200k Walk to the beach in minutes from Miramar Manor, a three-story oceanside estate along the sparkling coasts of Destin. This stunning 4-bedroom, 4 bathroom was fully remodeled in 2022. The home boasts over 4000 square feet of luxurious living space, perfect for entertaining family and friends.  The home includes a backyard pool and hot tub, multiple balconies, elevator, and an array of interior hangouts and amenities are all wrapped in upscale, airy design. You'll find the primary living area --- complete with tons of windows and a sleek fireplace. with billiards and an additional kitchen space are downstairs, while four curated bedrooms (some with private balconies!) give everyone plenty of room to make themselves at home. 
 
The premier location is just minutes from the Baytowne Marina, Sandestin Tennis Center, The Village of Baytowne Wharf.
